name: Phyllis Ginsberg
what_you_do: Phyllis Ginsberg provides guidance and tools to help people identify and replace obstacles hindering their well-being, with the goal of helping them go from surviving to thriving.
who_you_serve: People seeking to improve their lives and live their best life.
offering: Phyllis offers personalized work individually and in community, providing simple tools and practices that people can use on their own to retrain their brain and create a better life.
social_proof: Phyllis has worked with thousands of people and is the author of the best-selling book 'Empowered You'.
signature_programs: Phyllis has written several books, including 'Empowered You', 'Brain Makeover', and 'Tired and Hungry No More'.
business_focus: Helping people identify and replace obstacles hindering their well-being, with the goal of helping them go from surviving to thriving.
service_provided: Personalized coaching, workshops, speaking engagements, books
